        "formula": "Given X of shape (N, C_in, H, W), W of shape (C_in, C_out_per_group, K_H, K_W), parameters: stride=(S_H, S_W), padding=(P_H, P_W), dilation=(D_H, D_W), groups G. Let C_in_g = C_in // G, C_out_g = C_out // G. Output Y has shape (N, C_out, H_out, W_out) where H_out = (H-1)*S_H - 2*P_H + D_H*(K_H-1) + 1, W_out = (W-1)*S_W - 2*P_W + D_W*(K_W-1) + 1. For n in [0,N-1], oc in [0,C_out-1], i in [0,H_out-1], j in [0,W_out-1]: g = oc // C_out_g; Y[n,oc,i,j] = Σ_{ic=0}^{C_in_g-1} Σ_{kh=0}^{K_H-1} Σ_{kw=0}^{K_W-1} W[g*C_in_g+ic, oc%C_out_g, kh, kw] * X[n, g*C_in_g+ic, (i+P_H - kh*D_H)/S_H, (j+P_W - kw*D_W)/S_W] when (i+P_H - kh*D_H) is multiple of S_H and (j+P_W - kw*D_W) is multiple of S_W and the computed indices are within [0,H-1] and [0,W-1] respectively; otherwise the term is 0.",
